Combine Effect Estimates

grouped <- read_csv("./grouped_betas.csv")
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   variable = col_character(),
##   beta = col_double(),
##   method = col_character()
## )
ind <- read_csv("./ind_betas.csv")
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   variable = col_character(),
##   beta = col_double(),
##   method = col_character()
## )
plot_all <- rbind(grouped, ind) %>% filter(grepl("la$", variable))

Compare Variable Selection

plot_all %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = variable, 
                       y = round(beta, 5))) + geom_point(aes(color = method)) +
  theme_minimal() + geom_hline(yintercept = 0, color = "red", linetype = "dashed") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1), 
        legend.position = "bottom") +
  coord_flip() + 
  labs(title = "Variable Selection Coefficients", y = "Beta Coefficient",
       x = "Variable", color = "Method")

plot_all %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = method, 
                       y = round(beta, 5))) + geom_point(aes(color = method)) +
  theme_minimal() + geom_hline(yintercept = 0, color = "red", linetype = "dashed") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1), 
        legend.position = "bottom") +
  facet_wrap(.~variable) +
  coord_flip() + 
  labs(title = "Variable Selection Coefficients", y = "Beta Coefficient",
       x = "Variable", color = "Method")
